{"tid":1794280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【紓困措施】政府推出綠色生活本地遊計劃，每位接待資助１００元","createTime":"2019-12-23T04:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T07:51:02.000Z","uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67eba12354454e6ae4fe0ff4db8a7d5a891b6bcf","tid":1794280,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"【紓困措施】政府推出綠色生活本地遊計劃，每位接待資助１００元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社２３日專訊》政府宣布，預留５０００萬元推出為期６個月的「綠色生活本地遊」計劃，支援旅遊業。本港持牌旅行社在下月１日起，每接待一名本地遊客參加本地綠色旅遊，就可獲１００元資助，每間旅行社最多可獲５萬元資助。<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華表示，獲取資助條件簡單，旅行社要安排旅客到計劃指定的綠色景點，期間要聘用領隊及導遊，並要在行程中安排交通及食肆，希望可同時協助相關行業。<br />\n（ｃｗ）"},{"pid":"aa0a572aa8f9bdcd92dc5c8c3359bd1bc95df7d0","tid":1794280,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新德國聯署</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國聯邦議院《全球馬格尼茨基法案》</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲差44000人!!!!</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">目標50000人</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escap